            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> Marti Genio Victor<lb break="no" n="2"/>iae <expan><abbr>signif</abbr><ex>eri</ex></expan> ob immunitatem om<lb break="no" n="3"/>nem eis concessam a vicanis <lb n="4"/>veteribus consistentibus C<lb break="no" n="5"/><expan><abbr>astel</abbr><ex>lo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mattiac</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> Nov<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>anius Mo<lb break="no" n="6"/>getius Ianuarius Perp<supplied reason="lost">etuus</supplied> D<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">o</supplied>mati<lb break="no" n="7"/>us Bodico Seglatius S<supplied reason="lost">tatutu</supplied>s A<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">tessan</supplied><expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Montanus Senecianius Flor<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>ntinus Marti<lb break="no" n="9"/>onius Fortio Cossius Ner<supplied reason="lost">ti</supplied>nus Nertini<lb break="no" n="10"/>us Quintus Germanus Ibliae Isido<lb break="no" n="11"/>rius Severus Clau<supplied reason="lost">di</supplied>us Firmu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="12"/>Giamonius Adiuto<supplied reason="lost">r Iustu</supplied>s Censorin<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Vier aneinanderpassende Fragmente; bei der Auffindung waren sieben Fragmente erhalten. Zahlreiche Ligaturen. (B): Kohl: Z. 7 (Ende): I-longa nicht gelesen.</p>
            </div>
